2 NOTE The statement that Johann Wilhelm Achenbach was born in Germany apparently originated from statements that he was German. Isaac Achenbach of Cedar Co., IA reported that his grandfather came from Germa
3 CONC ny. The specific statement that he was from ***GAP*** Achenbach appears to have originated from Mary Ellen (Achenbach Wilcox) Miller. Given the following:
3 CONT 1) a Joh. Wilhelm Achenbach born on the exact date that everyone agrees for his birth recorded in the baptismal register at Saint John's Friedensburg;
3 CONT 2) Catherine Hehn was recorded at the same church;
3 CONT 3) the near proximity of Friedensburg and Pine Grove and
3 CONT 4) the lack of any other evidence of another Johann Wilhelm Achenbach in Schuylkill Co. leaves very little doubt as to his birth in Pennsylvania to a family of German language and origin.
