2 CONC l 8. Born in Lebanon September 4, 1920, she was the daughter of the late John E. and Laura S. Matterness Achenbach. She was a homemaker, member of North Annville Bible Church and enjoyed sewing and cr
2 CONC afts. In addition to her husband she is survived by her daughter Claudia A., wife of Donald Wise Sr. of Lebanon; son Eric D. Gettle of Lebanon; grandchildren Donnie Jr., husband of Dawn Wise, Randy, h
2 CONC usband of Barb Wise, and Tim, husband of Elizabeth Wise, all of Lebanon; and great-grandchildren Lauren, Caulen, Cayley, Hunter, and Amanda. She was preceded in death by brothers John, Ernest, Richard
2 CONC , and Claude Achenbach; and sisters Catherine Berkheiser, Alice Roof and Helen Berkheiser. Funeral Wednesday, May 16, at North Annville Bible Church. Interment at Kochenderfer Zion Cemetery. [Lebano
