2 CONT Florence Ruth Harnish Aughenbaugh (1896 - 1986)
2 CONT 
2 CONT Children:
2 CONT Pamela Aughenbaugh Nester (1948 - 2014)*
2 CONT 
2 CONT Burial: Prospect Hill Cemetery, York, York County, Pennsylvania, USA
