2 CONT MIDDLEBORO — Minnie Kessler, of Middleboro, passed away on Friday, December 12, 2014, a proud lifelong Westsider. Beloved wife of the late Louis M. Kessler. Loving mother of Richard Kessler of Rochest
2 CONC er and Robert Kessler & his wife Marcia of Rochester. Cherished grandmother of Jerzy and Nathaniel. Dear sister of the late Nathaniel Freedman and Daniel Freedman. Services Schlossberg Solomon Memoria
2 CONC l Chapel, 824 Washington St., Canton on Sunday, December 14 at 2:00PM. Interment to follow at the Beth El Cemetery, 776 Baker St., West Roxbury. Memorial observance at her late residence following th
2 CONC e burial on Sunday and continuing Monday, 4pm – 7pm. In lieu of flowers remembrances may be made to American Diabetes Association, 10 Speen St., 2nd floor, Framingham, MA 01701
2 CONT 
