2 CONC way. Dear father-in-law of Elaine, Mary and Lee. Dear brother of Louis Kessler of Middleboro, Florence Eaton of Millis and the late Bayla Kessler of Quincy. Dear brother-in-law of Minnie Kessler and R
2 CONC obert Eaton. Loving grandfather of Leah, Tyler, Alexandra, Mitchell and Margaux. Services at Schlossberg-Solomon Memorial Chapel, 824 Washington Street CANTON, on Monday, January 12, at 11:00 am. Memo
2 CONC rial observance will be at the home of Alan Kessler following interment until 4 pm and then from 6 pm-9 pm. In lieu of flowers remembrances in his memory may be made to Dana-Farber Institute, 10 Brook
2 CONC line Place West, 6th Floor, Brookline, MA 02445. Schlossberg-Solomon Chapel
